<para id="fs-idm349974416"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67884"/>Noren Company uses the balance sheet aging method to account for uncollectible debt on receivables. The following is the past-due category information for outstanding receivable debt for 2019.</para>
<media id="fs-idm343211744" alt="0–30 days past due, 31–90 days past due, and Over 90 days past due, respectively: Accounts Receivable amount $120,000, 80,000, 65,500; Percent uncollectible 7 percent, 20 percent, 40 percent; Total per category?; Total uncollectible?">
