</media>
<para id="fs-idm357048192">To manage earnings more favorably, Noren Company considers changing the past-due categories as follows.</para>
<media id="fs-idm359321984" alt="0–30 days past due, 31–90 days past due, and Over 90 days past due, respectively: Accounts Receivable amount $160,000, 50,500, 55,000; Percent uncollectible 7 percent, 20 percent, 40 percent; Total per category?; Total uncollectible?">
