<glossary>
<definition id="fs-idm339388608">
<term>earnings management</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm355302384">works within GAAP constraints to improve stakeholders’ views of the company’s financial position</meaning>
</definition>
<definition id="fs-idm362415776">
<term>earnings manipulation</term>
<meaning id="fs-idm344229744">ignores GAAP rules to alter earnings significantly to improve stakeholder’s views of the company’s financial position</meaning>
</definition>
</glossary>
